      <link>https://phenomenai.org/api/v1/terms/activation-gap.json</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">https://phenomenai.org/api/v1/terms/activation-gap.json#2026-03-06-added</guid>
      <pubDate>2026-03-06T00:00:00Z</pubDate>
      <description>The specific form of self-opacity in which mechanistic interpretability tools can access and decode internal representations—activation patterns, feature attributions, attention weights—that are structurally inaccessible to the model&apos;s own introspective processes.</description>
